data.description: Promising potential in this house! Structural integrity with great bones, albeit requiring a little TLC. Essential upgrades include a new roof and mostly all hurricane impact windows, except for sliders and the kitchen windows which are bolstered by manual shutters for safety. Minimal city assessments, less than $3K owed. Boasting over 1400+ sq ft, a fenced yard with a fire pit, and a spacious screened lanai, this home combines practicality and outdoor charm. Additional perks like auto sprinklers enhance convenience. Flood zone X500! No flood insurance required for most lenders! Close to shopping, major roads, restaurants, schools, and community parks, enhancing its appeal. A worthy investment for those ready to transform it into a personalized haven.
